Request Purpose  Authenticate user and receive authentication token for access to other methods.  Request Type  GET  Request Endpoint  /api/v0/auth/gettoken  Request Parameters     Parameter  Description      login  User login.    password  User password.     Request Example  https://app.byggeprojekt.dk/api/v0/auth/gettoken?login=iirsoft3&password=password  Response Example  {
    "statusMessage":"Success",
    "statusCode":200,
        "body":{
            "token":"13a6833433774dda8dd8ef8979d1180c",
            "expirationDate":"Jun 3, 2017 9:59:34 AM"
       }
}  Response Objects and fields     Parameter  Description      statusCode  Result code of request. Describes if request was successfully executed.    statusMessage  Description to statusCode.        body  Object with result for request.        token  Security token, should be used in next requests.    expirationDate  Expiration date of token.

Request Purpose  Get list of projects which are available for specified user.  Request Type  GET  Request Endpoint  /api/v0/project/getprojects  Request Parameters     Parameter  Description      token  Authentication token.     Request Example  https://app.byggeprojekt.dk/api/v0/project/getprojects?token=13a6833433774dda8dd8ef8979d1180c  Response Type:  json  Response Example  {
   "statusMessage":"Success",
   "statusCode":200,
        "body":{
            "projects":[
                {"id":1599,"name":"[02818] - P1"}
            ]
        }
}  Response Objects and fields     Parameter  Description      statusCode  Result code of request. Describes if request was successfully executed.    statusMessage  Description to statusCode.        body  Object with result for request.        projects  list with project objects.        id  Identifier of project.    name  Name of project.

Request Example  https://app.byggeprojekt.dk/api/v0/folder/getfolders?token=13a6833433774dda8dd8ef8979d1180c&projectid=1599  Response Example  {
       "statusMessage":"Success",
       "statusCode":200,
            "body":{
                "folders":[
                      {"id":74950,"name":"F1","projectId":1599},
                      {"id":76384,"name":"F2","projectId":1599}
                ]
       }
}

Request Example  https://app.byggeprojekt.dk/api/v0/folder/getfolders?token=13a6833433774dda8dd8ef8979d1180c&projectid=1599&parentfolderid=74950  Response Example  {
       "statusMessage":"Success",
       "statusCode":200,
            "body":{
                 "folders":[
                      {"id":76385,"name":"F1_1","parentFolderId":74950,"projectId":1599}
            ]
       }
  }

Request Example  https://app.byggeprojekt.dk/api/v0/folder/getfolders?token=13a6833433774dda8dd8ef8979d1180c&projectid=1599&all=true  Response Example  {
   "statusMessage":"Success",
   "statusCode":200,
        "body":{
             "folders":[
                  {"id":74950,"name":"F1","projectId":1599},
                  {"id":76385,"name":"F1_1","parentFolderId":74950,"projectId":1599},
                  {"id":76384,"name":"F2","projectId":1599}
        ]
   }
}  Response Objects and fields     Parameter  Description      statusCode  Result code of request. Describes if request was successfully executed.    statusMessage  Description to statusCode.        body  Object with result for request.    folders  List with folder objects.        id  Identifier of folder.    name  Name of folder.    parentFolderId  Identifier of parent folder.    projectId  Identifier of project.

