Request Purpose  Uploading document into system.  Request Type  POST  Request Endpoint  /api/v0/auth/upload  Request Parameters     Parameter  Description      token  Authentication token.    folderId  Identifier of folder into which should be uploaded files.    isLastFileInSession  Optional.  true  or  false  value for pointing if file or files last in upload session. If parameter not signed in request files will be uploaded like last in session    uploadSessionId  Optional. Required if some files was uploaded earlier and it is need upload files in the same upload session.     Also to request must be attached file parts.  Response Objects and fields     Parameter  Description      statusCode  Result code of request. Describes if request was successfully or unsuccessfully executed.    statusMessage  Description to statusCode.    body  Object with result for request.    uploadSessionId  Upload session identifier, should be used for next uploads in the same session.    documents  Array of document objects. See  document object     Example 1  Request  http://app.byggeprojekt.dk/api/v0/upload/uploadFile?token=218e104134ac40e584cec96bdd6089f5&folderId=40243&isLastFileInSession=true  Response     {
    "statusMessage":"Success",
    "statusCode":200,
    "body": {
        "documents":[{
            "id":153832,
            "name":"TEST_FILE.txt",
            "version":0,
            "parentFolderId":40243,
            "projectId":5376,
            "format":"",
            "scale":"",
            "revision_number":"",
            "fileSize":8,
            "uploadDate":"Aug 23, 2017 2:10:10 PM",
            "documentDescription":"",
            "documentCreator":"Jeff Beck - Company",
            "url":"http://download.byggeprojekt.dk/dwnl/download/Z6SyuLaWePVbY3Qhnw71LnXwedfdERbq5ivSgLtcx3ZN3aBooSIyuSmy9UwUraIASwxzF7s-IhL0u8xNw7O4WFuXr4AnXPkdOUdV4HnGTIDpV72BkQYxiMiOzojpYVU1Eoj4kK7EjLqnNXb1X5w1sw=="
        }]
    }
}  Example 2  Request  http://localhost:8888/byggeprojekt/api/v0/upload/uploadFile?token=218e104134ac40e584cec96bdd6089f5&folderId=40243&isLastFileInSession=false  Response     {
    "statusMessage":"Success",
    "statusCode":200,
    "body":{
        "uploadSessionId":"1503486877394"
    }
}  Error codes     Code  Message      401  Authentication problem    402  No  token  parameter    413  Wrong  folderid  parameter    416  Wrong  isLastFileInSession  parameter    417  No  folderid  parameter    421  No files attached    431  Current user have not permissions for uploading into folder    444  Application is not ready, try again after few minutes
